{"tid":1226342,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"麻煩華富的巴絲幫手尋貓","createTime":"2019-06-15T11:08:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T14:22:55.000Z","uid":79659,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a5257985ac8780c6eca86581a8ba890809362838","tid":1226342,"uid":79659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T11:08:41.000Z","msg":"貓貓叫Miruku <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fd73xBw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFd73xBw.png&h=3d4434bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係隻好細膽的貓女。昨晚（15/6）2030左右走左出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好擔心佢。佢未試過這樣出街<br />\n<br />\n落街搵左成晚仲未見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n麻煩華富華貴巴絲幫手留意下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［img]<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/YaoFzQ8.png[/img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYaoFzQ8.png%5B%2Fimg%5D&d=w67RnNhE2FzFZIT47vnPgBZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=319c73e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/YaoFzQ8.png[/img]</a><br />\n<br />\n貓貓有紅色頸圈<br />\n<br />\n有牛牛的毛色特徵<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e12K1wE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe12K1wE.png&h=8547d48b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C6aAoK1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC6aAoK1.png&h=231a2b92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n背部頸位有白環。<br />\n<br />\n煩請各位如有消息 WhatsApp 或致電62700830<br />\n<br />\n再次多謝各位有心人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1ac341d430512fb851a19532a6ace0ce087d894","tid":1226342,"uid":79659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T11:10:11.000Z","msg":"追加圖片<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AM1Ptc1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAM1Ptc1.png&h=2a2d37bb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0a3440fcb3fe46b90a611162a331a522b552dea4","tid":1226342,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T11:15:13.000Z","msg":"你係咪近燒烤場呀?<br />\n附近好多喵的"},{"pid":"367fcc89cb7b88d54373002f3c5f67af3e9d836d","tid":1226342,"uid":79659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a3440fcb3fe46b90a611162a331a522b552dea4","tid":1226342,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T11:15:13.000Z","msg":"你係咪近燒烤場呀?<br />\n附近好多喵的"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T11:18:18.000Z","msg":"依半年搬左去村囗。<br />\n貓貓冇出過街搬家後"},{"pid":"4a1ec6283b43f2c3a7f6175c0c7d4d1f0cd298ba","tid":1226342,"uid":177724,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T11:20:33.000Z","msg":"之前聽返嚟，唔知真定假，你買啲罐罐去餵流浪貓，順便同佢地講你係邊個邊個的主人，希望佢快啲返屋企。"},{"pid":"76ff379c887c5d417a168c7373820f31a4acbe6a","tid":1226342,"uid":79659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4a1ec6283b43f2c3a7f6175c0c7d4d1f0cd298ba","tid":1226342,"uid":177724,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T11:20:33.000Z","msg":"之前聽返嚟，唔知真定假，你買啲罐罐去餵流浪貓，順便同佢地講你係邊個邊個的主人，希望佢快啲返屋企。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T11:22:57.000Z","msg":"多謝你。我今朝都有做。希望得"},{"pid":"19b7c54f16f1f3dbc27d09df6b64084e633b09b3","tid":1226342,"uid":50744,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"367fcc89cb7b88d54373002f3c5f67af3e9d836d","tid":1226342,"uid":79659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a3440fcb3fe46b90a611162a331a522b552dea4","tid":1226342,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T11:15:13.000Z","msg":"你係咪近燒烤場呀?<br />\n附近好多喵的"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T11:18:18.000Z","msg":"依半年搬左去村囗。<br />\n貓貓冇出過街搬家後"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T11:23:01.000Z","msg":"村口可能走左落華貴<br />\ngood luck"},{"pid":"0cc67aeb2f9762bb5746bbe4a4e87f3d91d6dd08","tid":1226342,"uid":